title: Victory at Sea in MPEG1 format
description:
Hope this works. My first attempt at multple files.

All 26 shows of that 1952 series. Each is about 27 minutes and around 270MB.
I have basic DSL so it may take me a day or so to get it uploaded.
Hope others will upload as I do not have the bandwidth to keep it going indefinitely

If viewing in Windows Media Player turn up the brightness and turn down the contrast. WMP seems to give a dark picture in the default settings.
Now Playing>Enhancments>Video Settings
